  "notes": "Born 1516 in Warwickshire, England — during the reign of Henry VIII, one year before Martin Luther's 95 Theses. Mother: Alyce Merymoth (1520, Warwickshire). Married Alyce Merymoth. Resided in Bromley, Middlesex. Father of Thomas Copp (1539-1628). Died 1565 in Hatton, Warwickshire at age 49. His great-grandson William Copp emigrated to colonial Massachusetts in 1641."
